-- Iran’s Inflation Accelerated to 21.8% in 12 Months to April 19
-- B y   L a d a n e   N a s s e r i
-- 2012-05-15T07:08:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-15/iran-s-inflation-accelerated-to-21-8-in-12-months-to-april-19.html
Iran ’s rate of inflation quickened to
21.8 percent in the 12 months through the Iranian month of
Farvardin, which ended April 19, from 21.5 percent the previous
month, the  Central Bank  said today on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
